            "title": "滬指開市跌58點 深成指跌389點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地股市初段顯著向下，上證綜指以4,054點開市，跌58點或1.42%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指開市報15,729點，亦跌389點或2.41%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數跌93點，開報4,865點；創業板指數開市報4,135點，跌125點。</p>\n</div>",
