        {
            "title": "港股開市︱收復兩萬三 恒指回升190點報23,071點 芯片股逆市急回",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股在下半年首個交易日高開，恒生指數開市報23,071點，升190點或0.83%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生科技指數開報4,528點，升56點或1.25%；國企指數以7,613點開市，升54點或0.73%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股7.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股7.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">各車企相繼公布上月銷售數字，相關股份今早普遍跟隨大市高開。比亞迪(01211)開報76元，升4.9%；吉利汽車(00175)開報17.39元，升3.14%；理想汽車(02015)開報47.7元，升3.52%。蔚來(09866)開報39元，升0.67%；小鵬集團(09868)開報53.15元，升4.94%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：比亞迪官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2025/03/20240809_FI_source-web_01211-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：比亞迪官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2025/03/20240809_FI_source-web_01211-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：比亞迪官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">重磅股同樣升多跌少，滙控(00005)開報149.2元，升0.88%；友邦(01299)開報71元，跌0.63%。阿里巴巴(09988)開報95.3元，升2.64%；騰訊(00700)開報442.6元，升2.98%。京東(09618)ADR昨晚收市折合每股已重越百元關，該股今早在港甫開市即重獲「紅底股」身份，開報103元，升3.78%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：京東官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250218_FI_source-web_09618.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：京東官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250218_FI_source-web_09618.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：京東官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">半導體巨擘美光昨晚急挫逾10%，近期強勢的香港上市芯片及半導體相關股今早亦顯著下滑。中芯(00981)開報84.1元，回吐5.93%；華虹宏力(01347)開報199.9元，跌7.11%；兆易創新(03986)開報1,040元，急跌12.46%；ASMPT(00522)開報215元，也跌9.97%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">安克創新(00668)今日登場，以99.3元開市，較招股價99.32元低0.02%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16283537-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e6%94%b6%e5%be%a9%e5%85%a9%e8%90%ac%e4%b8%89-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%9b%9e%e5%8d%87190%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b123071%e9%bb%9e-%e8%8a%af%e7%89%87%e8%82%a1%e9%80%86",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-07-02 09:33:22",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "吉利6 月銷量按年升2%  出口升157%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">吉利汽車(00175)公布，6月汽車總銷量為240,799部，較去年同期增長約2%，首6 月銷量1,422,958部，按年升1%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2026/04/20260404_blog_source_web_chat6.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2026/04/20260404_blog_source_web_chat6.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">資料圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">其中極氪6 月銷量35,169輛，按年升111%，1至6 月累升176,370輛，按年升97% ; 吉利186,564輛，按年跌3%，首6 月1,100,373輛，按年跌5%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">純電動車6 月銷量按年升22%，半年跌10%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">6 月出口102,874輛，按年升157%，今年累計出口474,228部，按年升158%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16283247-%e5%90%89%e5%88%a96-%e6%9c%88%e9%8a%b7%e9%87%8f%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%8d%872-%e5%87%ba%e5%8f%a3%e5%8d%87157",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240508_FI_source-web_00175-4.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-07-02 09:33:22",
